Album: Awaken, My LoveArtiste: Childish GambinoGenre: R&amp;B and soulRelease: December 2, 2016This is Gambino's third studio album, which includes tracks sung rather than rapped. Gambino decides to make a musical shift from his usual hip hop style as he embraces a more musical side. The album is produced by both Donald Glover (Childish Gambino) and Ludwig Goransson. Essential tracks on the 11-track album include "Me and Your Mama," "Have Some Love," "Riot," "Redbone" and "Stand Tall". Childish Gambino explores a different dimension of music without confinement. He proves that he has a lot to offer. Brilliant. Star Rating: 3.5 out of 5